Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:37.25,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The year 2046
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:40.89,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,After the invention of a device called Neuro-Linker, most young people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:44.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,spent most of their lifetime in a virtual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:49.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A boy named Haruyuki, suffering from his bad social situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.85,0:00:54.03,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,received a strange program from the most popular girl of the school, Kuroyukihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.77,0:01:00.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll send you an application
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,for your Neuro-Linker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.60,0:01:11.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A program that changes one's reality completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:41.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Accelerated?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.95,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A world that is speeded up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:46.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The name of this application is "Brain Burst"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.70,0:01:50.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It accelerates the human brain by 1000 times.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Now, shout this: Burst Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Burst Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:01.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A second in the real world now consists of a thousand seconds for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Knowing the secret of the fast-paced world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.66,0:02:08.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki became the knight of Kuroyukihime to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:13.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to be faster, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:19.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is the story of a young man yielding a great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:27.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll make you dance with my 'Poison Sound'!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:36.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The only way to get "Burst Points" is through duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:39.71,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If a player loses all "Burst" points,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the program "Brain Burst" will be uninstalled,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and can't be re-installed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And the player's memories regarding "Brain Burst" will be erased entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.03,0:02:55.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If this world is so close to reality, he must have a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:00.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:04.73,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Dance more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Please move 'Silver Crow'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Faster than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:16.95,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Even if I can't trust myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:24.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Your consciousness has created that body, if you don't trust yourself, who will?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.25,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Are you able to stop my "Monster Machine"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I will believe in her words!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It is almost time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:45.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:52.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:55.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In order to keep accelerating
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:57.91,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,you must keep fighting and winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:02.33,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Again, congratulations on your first victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you can quickly ascend to level 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Currently I can't imagine leveling up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.99,0:04:13.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In fact, it is an unimaginable long path...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.05,0:04:19.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Within thousands of Burst Linkers, only few reach level 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:23.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If you reach level 7 or 8, you can go on and enter a large group.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:25.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A Group?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:31.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In other online games it's called "Guild", but we call it "Legion".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:37.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Currently, Accel World is divided and ruled by 6 legions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:41.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They are ruled by level 9 Burst Linkers which are,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:48.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Blue, Red, Yellow, Green, Purple and White.\NThey are the 6 Kings of pure color.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:52.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I never heard of any game where level 9 is the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.24,0:04:56.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I never said that level 9 is the maximum level.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So, is there anyone who is level 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:00.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:03.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In Brain Burst 2039,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:06.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,since its creation 7 years ago by a mysterious author,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:11.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,no one has reached level 10\Nmost likely due to the difficult conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.92,0:05:14.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Is it because you need dozens of wins?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:15.73,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A million maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Only 5 wins are needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:21.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But every opponent must be level 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:24.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And if he loses... he will run out of points.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Causing Brain Burst to be removed from the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,One summer, 2 years ago ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.44,0:05:34.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,everyone of the present kings reached level 9 almost at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and due to a message of the system, they knew the difficult condition to gain level 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:41.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,At one point a disastrous war arose because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:45.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,but up till now, the kings decided to abandon that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:49.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They signed an agreement and established a society with laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's a farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:56.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They must have defeated thousands of Linkers\N to get to level 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:06:02.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So, your goal is to challenge those kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No, I already did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:09.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The 6 kings, formerly 7 kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.67,0:06:14.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,had a strong bond and were friends and rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:18.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,but the black king betrayed the other kings,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,on that night two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The black king?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am the seventh queen "Black Lotus".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:28.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I was against the non-aggression pact,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.65,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and I proposed that we should fight among the 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:34.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Since then, Kuroyukihime disappeared from Accel World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:39.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But lately she has received challenges within the school network.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She was chased by a blue avatar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.71,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,called Cyan Pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She ended up asking Haruyuki for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And the suspect to be Cyan Pile was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:06:59.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Kurashima Chiyuri,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.97,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the childhood friend of Haruyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:04.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I-I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:16.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,However, he believed in the innocence of his friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.19,0:07:18.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So he went straight to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:21.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And so, he found the trojan on her Neuro Linker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.11,0:07:22.65,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thats weird. It's slow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:32.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could this be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.69,0:07:35.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}..a back door!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Burst Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.84,0:07:53.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The boy who attacked Haruyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Araya, attacked the two with a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.32,0:07:59.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,At that moment, Kuroyukihime used the second,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,to tell her feelings to Haruyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:04.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This must be revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I didn't try to understand the other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:09.73,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I played with the feelings of others up to this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:11.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:13.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Do not make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,At least all of this has something good to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:19.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Good?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.67,0:08:27.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,you will believe my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.77,0:08:31.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki-kun, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:34.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is a new feeling for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:36.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I can't control it, and I always feel confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I always think of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It fills me with joy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and also sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:46.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's what they call love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.65,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Be strong and become faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:54.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Show me you have the potential I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:55.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:58.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I can't let something happen to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:09:01.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I must protect you... but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:07.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I still... I haven't done anything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:17.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Someday... we'll see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai, don't do it ... Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.18,0:09:30.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Kuroyukihime saved Haruyuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.34,0:09:50.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and received a severe injury that left her unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.01,0:09:56.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If she receives a challenge from Cyan Pile while unconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.16,0:09:57.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,then I can't intervene and he wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:10:00.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:07.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The next day, his best friend, Takumu, appeared at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Taku, you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:11.25,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:14.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But what is his reason to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Burst Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.82,0:10:32.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The reason is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.14,0:10:36.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Takumu is Cyan Pile!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:39.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You placed the virus in Chiyuri's Linker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And you accessed her hard drive without permission, Taku!
Comment: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:45.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Needs Translation fix...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:46.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That you are the one to see through her hard drive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're not even her boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But you never truly know the girls you're with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:58.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She seemed to be happier with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:01.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,even when I held her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.98,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Everything needs to end, Haru.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Spiral Gravity Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:50.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The avatar of Takumu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:51.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Cyan Pile, is level 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:54.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow is only level 1, he stood no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Even so, Crow tries to get up for Kuroyukihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:02.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.61,0:12:03.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.67,0:12:07.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,True strength is not only to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:12.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Even if I look pathetic, I crashed into ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and being paralyzed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:16.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I have to fight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:19.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and continue to long for the sky even if I am grounded...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.65,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That is the sign of strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:29.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It was the awakening of his true ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:34.95,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Wings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:39.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She is calling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:05.97,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.89,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It was the ability to fly, which had never been given before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Fall off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Lightning Cyan Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:40.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:43.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:45.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:50.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You will be recognized in the world as the fastest Linker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And you will see the potential within our minds and hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:56.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The great potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I can see! I can see it, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:20.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:22.73,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You win, Haru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:34.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In the real world, I can't beat you in anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:37.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,but, in this world you can not beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Now, we are on the same level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's why... That's why you'll be my ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.12,0:14:46.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Be my ally, Taku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:51.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Just like me, you'll fight under the command of that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why would you trust me?
Comment: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Check Translation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:57.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I have betrayed the guidelines and my Legion,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I also betrayed my two only friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.72,0:15:05.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,From now on we'll talk together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:08.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,about Brain Burst and what we fight for...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:12.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And also of the feelings that we kept hidden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:14.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We will talk about everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.46,0:15:16.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I think we...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,need to start there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:41.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpa{\fscx150\fscy100}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:47.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Comment: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:54.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Check Translation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:54.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Good thing... I knew you would be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Haruyuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:01.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You told me to trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:09.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Your true appearance is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,My instinct wasn't wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You are the person who will change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The time has come, I must get out of my cocoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and fly to the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:59.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Listen! Burst Linkers dominated by the 6 Legions!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.95,0:17:01.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,My name is Black Lotus and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I challenge the 6 current kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:06.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,My legion Nega Nebulous and I,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.62,0:17:08.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's time to get out of our comfort zone and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,defy the false peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.33,0:17:13.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The appearance of Silver Crow with the ability to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:16.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and the announcement to restore Nega Nebulous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,spread quickly through the fast-paced world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:20.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Three months later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:24.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The territory, the area, that is dominated by a legion, is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:28.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,determined by the battle\Nthat occurs every Saturday in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:32.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A battle with unrestricted levels and number of participants.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.90,0:17:35.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You must win over 50% of the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We will take care of it, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:47.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you Haru, proceed as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:48.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You can count on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Cyan Pile joined Nega Nebulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:56.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The three people are securing the territories around the Suginami school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But, it was difficult to expand the territories further.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:05.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,His ability to fly was useless against long distance shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He didn't advance to level 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:10.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:12.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Did you think we would fall for the same thing twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:17.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Your flight ability, once you get used to it, you are an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:27.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Still, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.86,0:18:29.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.04,0:18:34.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:44.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,An angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:49.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A true angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:53.68,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,When he returned home he was greeted by a girl who claimed to be his cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I used the kitchen without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:19:01.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I thought you would be hungry when you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:08.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Can I also come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:13.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll leave! I am sorry! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:16.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we're cousins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.80,0:19:19.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No, sorry, I'm okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:27.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But, do not stare at me, please ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Tomoko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:46.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're a Burst Linker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The tan mark on your neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:20:01.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You are very observant if you realize those small details.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I got tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I 'll make you obey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:11.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You put Scarlet Rain in disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You will pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:17.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:45.98,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:50.98,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The identity of that Angel was Scarlet Rain, the Red King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She had investigated Haruyuki's real life,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:20:56.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,in order to enter his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Uh, are you really the Red King?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:24.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Rail Storm Domination!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:45.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow, Lightning Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I win, Onii-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:20.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So, will you listen to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:21.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.36,0:22:24.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I want to meet your leader...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:25.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:27.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.56,0:22:35.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why would you go to such lengths to meet Haruyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.18,0:22:38.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Do you love him that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:40.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:45.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I want his avatar, not him himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:47.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:52.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I want to borrow those wings on your back, your aviating ability, just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:55.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,to destroy the Calamity Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:22:58.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Calamity Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.14,0:23:07.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,VR movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:11.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's memory footage, played directly from inside my brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.97,0:23:15.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The Disaster Armor, also called "Chrome Disaster".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.14,0:23:17.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Seven Years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:20.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We tried to defend ourselves against it with everything we had...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:23.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,but even higher level Linkers were defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.75,0:23:26.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,However, they could not destroy the armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:30.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It is able to possess a Burst Linker...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:34.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It takes control of one's mind\Nand turns him into a killing machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.53,0:23:36.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:41.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is the fourth armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.63,0:23:45.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,His form and size are on a whole new level from the fifth one currently on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:48.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The armor changes its shape to fit its avatar host.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.16,0:23:52.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,However, its crazed manner of attack never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.67,0:24:07.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Two and a half years ago, thanks to the seven kings of pure color,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:11.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the curse of Chrome Disaster had been sealed, that's what we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:15.68,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,How do you explain what's happening now, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.29,0:24:19.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's a fact that a fifth one appeared and is on the loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.40,0:24:21.81,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What's the name of the fifth one?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:23.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Which of the kings is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.10,0:24:24.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's not a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.34,0:24:26.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The fifth one is my...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.64,0:24:30.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He's a member of the Red Legion, "Prominence".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.31,0:24:32.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Her original name is Cherry Rook.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.95,0:24:35.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He was a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.27,0:24:40.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He didn't have any flashy abilities, but he worked hard and got to level 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.77,0:24:42.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He had so much to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.09,0:24:43.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.52,0:24:45.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.15,0:24:51.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He still belongs to the Red Legion, but he goes around attacking the members of other Legions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:53.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He's breaking the non-aggression pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.03,0:24:59.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So now I have to deal with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:00.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.22,0:25:03.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I finally know what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.16,0:25:06.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Huh? What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.71,0:25:08.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.85,0:25:12.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I want you to catch Chrome Disaster for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.96,0:25:16.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.38,0:25:19.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We move forward with the plan the following afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:24.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Kuroyukihime and Nico decided to stay at Haru's house until the plan is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.59,0:25:36.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't stare at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.81,0:25:39.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This was the only color of stuff that would fit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.39,0:25:41.00,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.01,0:25:43.91,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It really suits you! It's perfect! It's a critical hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.35,0:25:46.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know Silver Crow?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.38,0:25:50.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She looks nice now, but without her clothes she's actually r-
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.07,0:25:55.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Is that the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.90,0:25:56.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You will see, I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.39,0:26:04.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Normally, members of different Legions are enemies, but
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.83,0:26:08.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the three of them laughed as if they were friends for a long time ...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.77,0:26:10.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Passing fun times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.15,0:26:21.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.23,0:26:26.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Cherry got on a train on the Seibu Ikebukuro line.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.45,0:26:30.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If he follows his usual pattern, he'll be hunting in Ikebukuro today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.02,0:26:31.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.20,0:26:35.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The mission to slay the fifth Chrome Disaster starts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.83,0:26:38.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Unlimited Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.60,0:26:43.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,S-So this is the Unlimited Neutral Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.91,0:26:44.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.94,0:26:47.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We used it before to hunt the Calamity Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.57,0:26:52.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you noticed anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.92,0:26:53.95,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.07,0:26:56.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There's no time limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.64,0:26:58.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.96,0:27:00.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's what makes it an unlimited field.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.01,0:27:05.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Once you're here, you can stay forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.26,0:27:09.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Of course, you have to be level 4 or above to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.89,0:27:32.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Before they arrived at Ikebukuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.44,0:27:36.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The Yellow King, Yellow Radio, appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.26,0:27:40.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I see. So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.87,0:27:43.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You planned all of this, Yellow Radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.80,0:27:45.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.43,0:27:48.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Let's go! Reinforced Exterior!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.88,0:27:59.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You punks are going to find out what it's like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.03,0:28:02.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,face the wrath of the Red King!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.64,0:28:05.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It all turned out to be the yellow king's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.51,0:28:09.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow and the others fell into his trap, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.24,0:28:11.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:16.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,ended up being a battle between level 9 Linkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.18,0:28:23.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I hated you from the first time we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.38,0:28:31.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Lotus!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.79,0:28:39.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Death by Piercing!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.74,0:28:43.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Fatal Fortune Wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.70,0:28:59.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The Calamity Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.21,0:29:01.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Chrome Disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.05,0:29:03.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.05,0:29:06.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We should've still had a day's worth of time in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.05,0:29:07.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.48,0:29:11.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He accelerated on the train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.26,0:29:19.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Deceit Firecracker!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.57,0:29:23.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Get devoured!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.68,0:29:25.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Get devoured and become my meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.40,0:29:40.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't even a fight anymore!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.69,0:29:45.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Chrome Disaster suddenly appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.15,0:29:47.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and the Yellow Legion retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.92,0:29:55.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.95,0:29:57.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.85,0:30:02.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow seeing all the power that individual had...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.26,0:30:03.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,lost the will to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.80,0:30:09.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,"A Burst Linker with no will to fight\Ncan't operate their Duel Avatar".
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.68,0:30:15.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're afraid of defeat, because you believe it will negatively affect your value.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.65,0:30:20.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's why you haven't been performing very well in the territory battles recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.75,0:30:22.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a belief. It's the truth.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.50,0:30:24.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.78,0:30:25.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't misjudge yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.12,0:30:30.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I won't abandon you, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.61,0:30:35.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Do you really think the bond between us...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.88,0:30:37.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,is that weak?!
Comment: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:44.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Check translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.30,0:30:44.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the words of Black Lotus, with whom he has an almost familiar bond,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.64,0:30:46.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow rose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.94,0:31:08.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.70,0:31:17.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.57,0:31:20.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is why i hate kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:22.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,S-Senpa{\fscx150}-
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.84,0:31:30.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She didn't shoot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.58,0:31:31.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She's just sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.58,0:31:31.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.97,0:31:37.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That little girl wants to trust, more than anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.31,0:31:39.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the final bond between Burst Linkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.47,0:31:43.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.29,0:31:45.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They're Parent and Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.48,0:31:48.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The Red King is Disaster's...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.64,0:31:51.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I mean, Cherry Rook's Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.83,0:31:56.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Well, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.52,0:31:57.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.28,0:32:00.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Go and help Niko.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.04,0:32:02.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Our ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.35,0:32:05.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.97,0:32:15.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.80,0:32:25.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So that edge at Sunshine City is the leave point.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.38,0:32:27.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If he's in the middle of a leap,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.22,0:32:29.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,you can't dodge me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:37.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What now? How do I stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.65,0:32:40.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.24,0:32:46.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,More!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.38,0:32:48.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I have to accelerate more!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.53,0:33:11.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.44,0:33:13.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,...want to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.51,0:33:15.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.34,0:33:18.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.97,0:33:20.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to be strong too?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.84,0:33:24.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You think that means you can be forgiven for everything you did?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.29,0:33:25.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.96,0:33:30.98,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Who doesn't want the strength to face every hardship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:33:59.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You did it, Silver Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.85,0:34:03.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.58,0:35:16.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's a Transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.57,0:35:19.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The Unlimited Neutral Field is of the Chaos element.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.78,0:35:23.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And so, it changes at specific intervals.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.97,0:35:27.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They cleared their item storage of the Calamity Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.43,0:35:30.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Then Silver Crow and the others returned to reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.93,0:35:41.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Haru?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.30,0:35:44.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,N-No, nothing's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.38,0:35:49.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I'm sorry, but one of my colleague's kids is staying over at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.76,0:35:51.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Well, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.49,0:35:56.00,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,My prized collection again...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.28,0:36:01.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.54,0:36:06.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Scarlet Rain told the Kings that Chrome Disaster was taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.28,0:36:10.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Cherry Rook, lost her memories of being a Burst Linker,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.73,0:36:12.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,but she had regained her common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.83,0:36:15.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.56,0:36:18.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Well, uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.63,0:36:20.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.65,0:36:22.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,C-Can I...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.54,0:36:24.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Can I really have these?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.25,0:36:26.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What?! If you don't want 'em give them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.29,0:36:28.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No, I'll have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.65,0:36:30.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.64,0:36:36.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They're good, Nico.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.50,0:36:39.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.66,0:36:46.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell are you crying for, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.89,0:36:48.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.24,0:36:50.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What's with you, you stupid idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.57,0:36:52.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't eat and cry at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.94,0:36:57.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The young man with silver wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.38,0:37:01.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,begins to grow by facing several Burst Linkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.30,0:37:04.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I will also enter Nega Nebulous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.75,0:37:06.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Kurashima Chiyuri, Lime Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.66,0:37:11.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,recommended by Scarlet Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.70,0:37:13.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The right hand of the Red King,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.30,0:37:15.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Kakei Mihaya, Blood Leopard.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.17,0:37:18.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In this world there are fateful encounters...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.52,0:37:20.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,and also strong bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.94,0:37:23.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Kurasaki Fuuko, Sky Raker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.99,0:37:27.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll show you everything about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.32,0:37:28.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,to the last drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.08,0:37:31.63,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Himi Akira, Aqua Current.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.71,0:38:16.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And so Silver Crow began to head towards the top of the accelerated world with Black Lotus next to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.84,0:38:19.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,through battles with more powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.03,0:38:22.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,176)}End of editing, timing and translation fixes by Knigh7s (borrowed subs from ??? for Chrome Disaster arch)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.84,0:40:10.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frame Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.30,0:40:16.25,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.37,0:40:20.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.92,0:40:30.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I won't let them take this point!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.59,0:40:34.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Today I will knock you out! You'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.78,0:40:35.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Raker!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.70,0:40:41.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.37,0:40:43.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frame Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.33,0:40:50.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.82,0:41:00.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Special Technique: Point Impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.80,0:41:22.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Using those legs is cheating...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.00,0:41:26.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You're stupidly obvious in your attacks, Ken-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.36,0:41:33.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Onee!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.58,0:41:34.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.33,0:41:41.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,How could you do that to my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.03,0:41:54.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.86,0:42:14.81,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They conquered the Meijijinguu temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.51,0:42:17.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We can't lose here!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.03,0:42:24.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The woman who has a tree avatar is recharging the energy of her allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.59,0:42:26.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That Decurion creates an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.30,0:42:30.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's considered bad luck to use a Christmas tree in august.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.94,0:42:32.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.66,0:42:36.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't summon my invincible fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.61,0:42:38.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Rain, can you make a crater on the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.85,0:42:40.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It will take about 20 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.26,0:42:42.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What do we gain by doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.14,0:42:44.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I have no time to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.71,0:42:46.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Okay, cover me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.00,0:42:47.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Shape Change.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.73,0:42:54.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,10... 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.60,0:42:59.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,18... 19...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.08,0:43:01.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.30,0:43:03.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hey, there I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.80,0:43:08.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's useless, you can't use that weapon against my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.36,0:43:27.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's cheating!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.85,0:43:38.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I hate the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.92,0:43:45.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In the basement there is a train tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.91,0:43:47.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You should have said that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.52,0:44:12.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, you damn crow!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.00,0:44:17.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You have the guts to face me, Bitter Valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.55,0:44:19.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I already told you that isn't Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.76,0:44:24.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's Igaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.71,0:44:27.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.77,0:44:38.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Technique V!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.65,0:45:01.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Very careless, Silver Crow.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.06,0:45:03.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.50,0:45:11.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The Green King, Green Grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.46,0:45:14.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Shibuya was part of our territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.15,0:45:17.63,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Give it back to me, Grande.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.06,0:45:20.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't look back to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.16,0:45:23.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We won't leave this territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.42,0:45:24.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.33,0:45:34.03,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Come to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.67,0:45:35.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.52,0:45:36.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.35,0:45:39.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If they fight between the kings it will be like 'Sudden Death'.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.54,0:45:44.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You see.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.90,0:45:45.95,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No, it's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.60,0:45:53.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A field change?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.60,0:45:53.18,N.T,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.11,0:45:54.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.12,0:45:57.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The battlefield territory does not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.82,0:46:09.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,W-What that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.19,0:46:15.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's a wind vortex?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.95,0:46:16.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.20,0:46:19.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.43,0:46:29.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,S-Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.11,0:46:43.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.13,0:47:02.63,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,S-Senpai, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.40,0:47:03.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No lo sé.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.79,0:47:07.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The network was never down before.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.22,0:47:08.89,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What happend?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.45,0:47:11.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That black tornado.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.96,0:47:14.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This effect is not possible with this wind speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.57,0:47:17.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The BB icon on the virtual desktop is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.67,0:47:24.73,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It does not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.99,0:47:25.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Burst Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.30,0:47:27.03,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Burst Link!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.97,0:47:28.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Rays...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.69,0:47:30.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,W-We can not accelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.75,0:47:32.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hey! And now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.48,0:47:45.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The social cameras in the city are out of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.67,0:47:47.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The area without service is expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.16,0:47:52.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's confirmed that Shijuko, Minato, Shinagawa and a part of Suginami,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.97,0:47:55.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,are in the same state.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.44,0:47:58.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The police was sent to the affected areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.81,0:48:01.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They are now investigating the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.87,0:48:03.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,At this moment they are on alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.16,0:48:07.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Citizens in the affected area are careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.54,0:48:09.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Guys, I'm sorry I called you on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.26,0:48:12.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.60,0:48:23.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,First, I want you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.77,0:48:32.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Leopard and Fuuko collected the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.45,0:48:34.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It is impossible to accelerate in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.29,0:48:36.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It keeps expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.97,0:48:40.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is the area without service.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.65,0:48:44.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They concur.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.79,0:48:47.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It is not possible that it is a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.27,0:48:50.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They must be some link.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.20,0:48:51.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The problem is...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.19,0:48:55.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It could be that we can't accelerate because the social cameras are malfunctioning,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.82,0:49:00.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,or the Brain Burst program is affecting the social cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.17,0:49:01.79,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.41,0:49:06.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If it's the first, we can not do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.94,0:49:11.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If it is the second, we can investigate in the accelerated world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.73,0:49:13.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,And what will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.62,0:49:18.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible to accelerate because the social cameras are off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.13,0:49:21.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I got an idea, we could walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.31,0:49:24.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We can enter the limited field from Suginami.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.17,0:49:25.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.57,0:49:32.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I heard that Burst Linkers were disconnected when they were touched by the black cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.82,0:49:36.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't you think we should discuss\Nthat with the other legions as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.93,0:49:40.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Obviously, I've asked for a meeting of the 7 Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.35,0:49:44.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But, because of the broken connection,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.46,0:49:47.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I got no answers from kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.62,0:49:50.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There is another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.04,0:49:53.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Guessing by its speed of expansion,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.80,0:50:00.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,this area will be devoured by the black cloud at 6 a.m.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.53,0:50:03.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It will isolate us from the accelerated world.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.76,0:50:04.81,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Very fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.93,0:50:09.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I plan to wait for the response of the kings until that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.09,0:50:12.81,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But, if they still don't respond...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.50,0:50:15.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We, the legion Nega Nebulous...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.39,0:50:17.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,we will face that black cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.18,0:50:18.91,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.39,0:50:20.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.91,0:50:24.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Tonight the members of our Legion will gather in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.03,0:50:26.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It would be good for us to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.99,0:50:29.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Is there a suitable place?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.75,0:50:37.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,My mother is traveling abroad for work, so if you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.65,0:50:41.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Thank you, the truth that wanted to ask for this favor from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.88,0:50:45.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So we'll meet at Haru's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.47,0:50:47.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll tell the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.81,0:50:49.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Ah, by the way, today is...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.29,0:51:21.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But they are not real, they are AR.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.93,0:51:24.27,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You'll never give up on her, don't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.51,0:51:27.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.06,0:51:28.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.21,0:51:34.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I was thinking, if this was okay while the accelerated world is in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.40,0:51:36.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But, it was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.45,0:51:38.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Everyone enjoys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.47,0:51:47.00,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki-kun, have you ever wondered what it would be like to stop being a Burst Linker?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.99,0:51:51.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I can not imagine it very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.06,0:51:53.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm just scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.27,0:51:56.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I understand, I'm scared too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.07,0:52:04.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Those who lose all their points, lose the memories of being a Burst Linker.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.04,0:52:09.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Besides I thought that one day this would be of help.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.81,0:52:14.73,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But if all social cameras in Tokyo are disabled,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.49,0:52:18.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,we are no longer able to be Burst Linkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.66,0:52:22.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But we are keeping our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.13,0:52:26.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I never imagined it to end this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.55,0:52:30.03,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's good that everyone gathered here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.98,0:52:34.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Even if we may spent too much time playing around before the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.24,0:52:37.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Fuuko, Utai and Nico as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.70,0:52:40.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They do not say it, but they are afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.52,0:52:45.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,that the bonds that we have disappear in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.14,0:52:50.97,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.36,0:53:02.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We are stubborn, we won't abandon the accelerated that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.43,0:53:04.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You also said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.54,0:53:08.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That if we don't withdraw that night we'll be feed to the dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.81,0:53:14.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Even if we can no longer return to the accelerated world, we will remain to be Burst Linkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.40,0:53:20.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The link that unites you, us and others will not disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.72,0:53:21.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.79,0:53:24.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I was lonely until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.07,0:53:26.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I thought I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.23,0:53:26.97,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.97,0:53:29.65,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I wasn't interested in reality, I only cared about virtual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.31,0:53:32.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I was so pathetic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.84,0:53:32.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.50,0:53:33.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.28,0:53:52.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,N-N-No, It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.11,0:53:53.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.70,0:53:57.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I am sorry! I am sorry! I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.17,0:54:01.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Haruyuki-kun, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.87,0:54:05.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.37,0:54:08.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I had a futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.26,0:54:12.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Eh?! What... What are you even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.44,0:54:15.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.99,0:54:16.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.26,0:54:26.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I didn't receive any messages from the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.33,0:54:32.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is the first major mission we have since Prominence and Nega Nebulous work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.52,0:54:34.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But it won't be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.83,0:54:38.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We will find out about the secret behind the black cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.29,0:54:41.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is a battle to keep moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.39,0:54:45.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We don't know which enemies await us, but nonetheless
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.92,0:54:47.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,we will defeat them and come back safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.81,0:54:50.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Unlimited Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.52,0:55:03.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.90,0:55:06.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's the same cloud I saw in the last territorial battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.77,0:55:11.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That is, if it devours us that thing will automatically disconnect us?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.24,0:55:13.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But what....
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.84,0:55:16.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.96,0:55:19.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What are you doing all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.37,0:55:23.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You know how my sister feels and you're still flirting with Lotus-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.67,0:55:25.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You fucking pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.93,0:55:28.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Onii-san, you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.32,0:55:29.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.19,0:55:31.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We don't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.75,0:55:38.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So we will proceed as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.55,0:55:40.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Appear, invincible fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.61,0:56:10.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Heat Blast Saturation!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.10,0:56:19.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn, the information was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.60,0:56:21.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But he does react.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.39,0:56:23.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I think we can get by while they attack that cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.75,0:56:27.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,With my machine it is easy-come and easy-go!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.76,0:56:29.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.51,0:56:33.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Then, we must do it as we discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.88,0:56:36.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So this or that way we have to enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.39,0:56:38.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Only we can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.89,0:56:41.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.34,0:56:47.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The green king, Green Grande?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.39,0:56:48.33,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He arrived on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.56,0:56:53.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.26,0:56:56.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I remember that cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.76,0:56:59.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,T-Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.06,0:57:01.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You know it, Grande?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.47,0:57:05.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It is the Dark Cloud of an old enemy, the Goddess Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.27,0:57:07.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Nukes?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.50,0:57:09.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But he was sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.56,0:57:14.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But Nukes did not have the ability to disconnect Burst Linkers.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.46,0:57:15.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Nukes?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.99,0:57:16.81,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Sealed?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.57,0:57:22.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The situation is complicated, we need to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.51,0:57:26.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So, can you go through that cloud?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.90,0:57:29.98,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Parsek Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.29,0:57:36.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A new technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.90,0:57:48.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That's great, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.56,0:57:51.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Seriously you're an old guy without grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.43,0:57:54.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We have no other option, we will have to trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.13,0:57:57.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Change, Dreadnought!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.90,0:58:31.51,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.25,0:58:37.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Here we go! Do not fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.69,0:58:40.57,N.T,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Note: (Talisman) Protection regarding traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.24,0:58:51.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Thank you for using our transport service.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.16,0:58:55.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Our transport vehicle will destroy objects along the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.12,0:58:58.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,to collect energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.98,0:59:02.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I hope you don't fall off.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.50,0:59:09.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,A world were everyone protects himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.88,0:59:14.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This was a warning from the Scarlet Rain society for safe transport!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.00,0:59:20.00,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.70,0:59:24.14,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The cloud area begins in Opera City, there we will enter the Dark Cloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.55,0:59:26.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Now is your turn, Grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.01,0:59:39.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Parsek Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.08,0:59:47.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Will we be all right, Grande-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.21,0:59:49.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We're 2 minutes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.64,0:59:50.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.73,0:59:52.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Is that the limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.04,1:00:00.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You should have told us earlier...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.47,1:00:02.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,To all engines!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.07,1:00:07.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Ni-Rain, go on, go on!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.00,1:00:15.91,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The shield seems to be weakening.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.45,1:00:16.79,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,10
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.76,1:00:18.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,9
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.72,1:00:19.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,8
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.94,1:00:20.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,7
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.09,1:00:22.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why are you counting?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.18,1:00:23.33,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Rain!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.63,1:00:25.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm already at it!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.49,1:00:25.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,4
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.31,1:00:26.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,3
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.42,1:00:27.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,2
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.49,1:00:29.15,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.80,1:00:44.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.64,1:00:47.34,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.26,1:01:07.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's like an Olympic stadium?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.84,1:01:08.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.38,1:01:49.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.92,1:01:51.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,These are subordinates of Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.14,1:01:53.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Nukes Core.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.54,1:01:55.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That place is like their base.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.63,1:01:58.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They're protecting the stadium.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.19,1:02:03.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So, the Goddess of Night, Nukes, was exempt from the seal,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.62,1:02:04.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,is in there.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.95,1:02:07.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate, we'll commence the attack.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.73,1:02:09.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Rain, attack with everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.40,1:02:10.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The others follow Rain!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.11,1:02:11.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.71,1:02:24.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Too many.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.51,1:02:29.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I got this!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.12,1:02:34.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Eat shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.00,1:02:36.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Heat Blast Saturation!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.55,1:02:39.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,He stopped!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.68,1:02:41.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.69,1:02:44.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,They hit me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.80,1:02:50.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai, the Goddess Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.45,1:02:53.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She was the strongest enemy of the underground of Yoyogi.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.08,1:02:58.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But since she was very dangerous, she and that dungeon were sealed.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.06,1:02:59.82,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It was forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.54,1:03:01.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Very dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.00,1:03:04.89,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She is a legendary level enemy which we once fought.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.85,1:03:08.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,She has a power greater than Shisei Metatron.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.59,1:03:13.29,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why did she appear now?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.14,1:03:15.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frame Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.96,1:03:16.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.02,1:03:17.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.80,1:03:18.71,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Maelstrom.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.45,1:03:24.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Freeze Trans.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.01,1:03:50.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frame Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.97,1:03:53.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There is no end to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.80,1:03:56.06,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It is useless to just brute force.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.71,1:03:57.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.84,1:03:59.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn, they surrounded me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.94,1:04:00.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Rain.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.87,1:04:08.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I can't use the missiles!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.03,1:04:13.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If they defeat us here...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:14.07,1:04:16.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,they will continue forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.24,1:04:19.63,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.93,1:04:23.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Rain!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.48,1:04:33.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This technique...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.89,1:04:51.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You are Aster Vine and this is the purple king, Purple Thorn.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.65,1:04:52.00,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.77,1:04:55.03,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We did not come to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.58,1:04:57.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We came because Grande asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.49,1:05:02.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Can't you help us more carefully?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.86,1:05:05.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Then I can't help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.14,1:05:07.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There they come again!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.59,1:05:08.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Chie-chan, stay behind!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.30,1:05:21.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I see you like to go solo, Black Lotus.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.99,1:05:24.33,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The blue king, Blue Knight.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.22,1:05:26.89,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,How did they get here?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.28,1:05:28.64,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Thank Grande.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.63,1:05:34.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If he hadn't opened the road, we wouldn't have been able to pass.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.49,1:05:37.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's why they look like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.92,1:05:38.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You and your companions.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.34,1:05:39.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.02,1:05:44.17,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Regardless I think I'm better than you.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.56,1:05:47.02,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,In addition, the true hero is late.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.73,1:05:48.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Right, Lotus?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.44,1:05:51.33,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I know you don't get along with others.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.86,1:05:54.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Do not you think this time it would be better to help us?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.92,1:05:57.94,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What do you say? Damn, since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.94,1:06:00.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Senpai, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.64,1:06:04.35,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Bell, help the Kings recover.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.04,1:06:11.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hello, excuse me, this way, this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.07,1:06:13.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Come closer.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.68,1:06:14.65,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That is good.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.23,1:06:16.47,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.35,1:06:23.25,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Citron Call!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.51,1:06:29.16,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So this is the recover ability.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.94,1:06:31.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I did not think I would get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.69,1:06:35.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Refresh, refresh.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.76,1:06:40.43,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That was it. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.49,1:06:45.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Lotus, you will make no progress if you keep fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.92,1:06:46.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I-It's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.52,1:06:50.24,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,These flying dragons are everyone's enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.04,1:06:54.28,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We must strike with ranged attacks to make them fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.88,1:06:55.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.65,1:06:56.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.89,1:06:57.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Nega Nebulous.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.23,1:07:04.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.18,1:07:06.68,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Coronal Mass Ejecution!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.61,1:07:10.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Vorpal Strike!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.84,1:07:12.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Lightning Cyan Spike!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.67,1:07:14.56,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Superluminal Stroke!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.74,1:07:15.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frontal Thunder!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.02,1:07:16.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Maelstrom.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.30,1:07:20.71,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Laser Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.19,1:07:38.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Keep moving, there only 2 left.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.46,1:08:05.18,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Chie-chan!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.18,1:08:13.76,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.69,1:08:20.07,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Taku!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.47,1:08:28.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn, damn, damn.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.43,1:08:30.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,At this rate, Taku will be forever lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.36,1:08:42.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.27,1:08:50.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Do not tell me that...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.20,1:08:59.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Wow, wow, it's an ugly view.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.78,1:09:01.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's ugly.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.89,1:09:02.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yellow Radio.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.15,1:09:05.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I do not like to do these things, but
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.29,1:09:09.33,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,there's no problem with me helping you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.78,1:09:11.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.69,1:09:14.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You followed us without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.01,1:09:16.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Don't act so mighty!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.20,1:09:18.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I do not know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.06,1:09:20.42,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.69,1:09:44.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Great, all 6 Kings gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.02,1:09:48.49,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes, I never imagined to see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.28,1:09:50.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Silver Crow.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.20,1:09:51.74,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.20,1:09:54.59,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We will take care of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.57,1:09:57.48,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You'll fly with your queen.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.45,1:10:00.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.54,1:10:03.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We will clear the sky.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.97,1:10:04.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Let's cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.30,1:10:06.03,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.05,1:10:08.37,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's time to fight back!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.93,1:10:09.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.13,1:10:15.68,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Set On!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.79,1:10:17.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Gale Thurster!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.30,1:10:49.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.70,1:10:51.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Halistorm Domination!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.70,1:10:57.05,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frame Torrent!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.39,1:11:00.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:01.26,1:11:01.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.08,1:11:03.71,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Frame Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.38,1:11:19.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,How are you, Crow?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.05,1:11:22.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Go and give that thing a good beating!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.36,1:11:30.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Where are we, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.19,1:11:33.53,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the bottomless space.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.33,1:11:34.89,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.19,1:11:57.81,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.86,1:12:00.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,the one I saw...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.32,1:12:02.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Do not wake us up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.39,1:12:05.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Are they the ones generating that black cloud?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.00,1:12:12.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That black cloud will cause eternal sleep in the fast-paced world.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.27,1:12:17.80,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Then nobody will fight, there will be no sadness and no one will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.73,1:12:24.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,All Burst Linker will fall into a sweet dream and can live forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.03,1:12:27.11,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That would not be living.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.69,1:12:30.66,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Burst Linkers that do not accelerate, are no longer Burst Linker.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.35,1:12:34.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Then stay here forever too.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.80,1:12:38.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Keep accelerating until eternity in this garden.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.94,1:12:44.98,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.28,1:12:48.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I feel something coming in...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.84,1:12:55.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is.. her memory...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.12,1:13:06.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Unlimited Burst!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.98,1:13:13.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Your little, but very sad, cry
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.92,1:13:17.04,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,awakened me from my thousand years of sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.99,1:13:20.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.48,1:13:23.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I failed...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.91,1:13:26.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Sure in the real world, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.68,1:13:38.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I was always afraid to fly.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.80,1:13:44.52,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But I trained in the accelerated world and worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.23,1:13:47.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Finally the people had accepted me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.14,1:13:52.72,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If I can not fly, I'm no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.88,1:14:17.58,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.90,1:14:27.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,How foolish! Is that why you're still in this unlimited field?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.92,1:14:33.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes, we will never return to the Lowest Level.\NI will fall asleep for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.32,1:14:35.83,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,That is your wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.38,1:14:37.36,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Laser Sword!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.98,1:14:38.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.28,1:14:42.92,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We are not enemies, this isn't the world where we should live.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.14,1:14:47.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,People who try to wake her up will be devoured at night.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.42,1:14:56.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.89,1:15:16.38,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.73,1:15:19.87,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,So this is the true form of Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.49,1:15:21.75,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.13,1:15:23.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If we go further, we will be caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.05,1:15:24.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.61,1:15:33.84,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai, what about them?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.15,1:15:35.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I heard about them.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.59,1:15:36.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Nemesis and Tanatus.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.11,1:15:38.90,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The sons of Nukes are the powerful enemies.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.24,1:15:43.68,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Their damage is collateral.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.42,1:15:44.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.82,1:16:02.95,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why do you take so long?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.49,1:16:04.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Metatron?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.93,1:16:05.54,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You saved us.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.11,1:16:07.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Shut up, immature being!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.05,1:16:12.19,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Damn, I can not keep watching, it's so silly.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.74,1:16:14.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Come closer, my subordinate Silver Crow.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.61,1:16:20.50,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's true that with your current strength you can't defeat Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.50,1:16:21.70,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Useless, nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.70,1:16:23.85,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.13,1:16:25.10,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But still.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.71,1:16:29.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,The circuit that unites Nukes with those warriors,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.05,1:16:33.21,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,is weaker than our bond.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.92,1:16:37.93,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You must separate the little white warriors until you can break that circuit.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.51,1:16:40.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But I do not have the strength to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.37,1:16:43.69,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.49,1:16:49.20,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It's not strength, use your heart and with your new energy source you should be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.02,1:16:59.41,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,You must defeat those two guardians and Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.89,1:17:01.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,My subordinate Silver Crow,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.70,1:17:02.77,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,use your wings!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.63,1:17:03.96,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.29,1:17:06.26,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Senpai, help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.68,1:17:06.91,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.31,1:17:07.88,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There they come.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.07,1:17:12.13,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Light Speed!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.39,1:17:22.08,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We got through!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.74,1:17:24.09,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Metatron Wing!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.40,1:17:48.55,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Laser Lance Vorpal Strike!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.42,1:18:09.40,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.33,1:18:12.86,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,We must return to the real world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.53,1:18:17.31,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Beloved people are awaiting us.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.96,1:18:21.60,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I was always alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.35,1:18:25.23,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There is no one who waits for me in the real world.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.10,1:18:27.78,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Gymnastics was everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.63,1:18:31.44,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,It was the only thing that connected me to people.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.26,1:18:35.71,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to lose everything and suffer alone...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.45,1:18:38.32,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'd rather fall asleep forever here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.67,1:18:39.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I used to think the same way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.91,1:18:46.30,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Once I thought I could never get up again after losing everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.07,1:18:51.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But he and my companions taught me that I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.18,1:19:00.22,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,If you stretch your out your hand you can reach anyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.88,1:19:04.57,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,There must be someone waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.38,1:19:06.61,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.18,1:19:23.67,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.64,1:19:30.39,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I'm coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.24,1:19:31.46,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.24,1:19:34.45,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Sorry and thanks, Nukes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.07,1:19:36.62,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,But that is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.76,1:19:41.12,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,I will be watching over you at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.40,1:19:42.99,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.32,1:20:07.01,SubtitleS,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for us to come with so many people?
